{"tid":2109380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會：強國選民未能來港投票 政府：會安排","createTime":"2020-07-15T08:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T09:31:14.000Z","uid":116989,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ac623587e99c8f7f1fe27dc78bf01a5ed6ff64","tid":2109380,"uid":116989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>工聯會稱疫情下數以十萬計海外選民未能返港投票</strong><br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員黃國健指，現時疫情嚴重，9月的立法會換屆選舉，數以十萬計身在海外的本港選民受疫情影響，可能未能返港投票，認為會嚴重影響他們的政治權利，希望政府關注及思考如何處理有關問題。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>至於是否認為選舉應押後，黃國健指目前任何可能性都要考慮。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n曾國衞早上在立法會內務委員會上指，因應疫情反覆，<strong>當局正為九月立法會換屆選舉，制定不同的方案</strong>，要讓市民行使選舉權利，亦要考慮公共衛生安全。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347171/工聯會海外選民疫情下難回港投票-曾國衞正協商居內地港人投票安排\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2347171%2F%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E9%9B%A3%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%8D%94%E5%95%86%E5%B1%85%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=014bab9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347171/工聯會海外選民疫情下難回港投票-曾國衞正協商居內地港人投票安排</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182cbb0bd39552afb6707d2a9b36063cf5399073","tid":2109380,"uid":116989,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"原來何妖又嗌緊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gCoJ7H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gCoJ7H.png&h=d01b21d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衫人著曬草，所以唔准選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf057b581f0cbb0f90e349e45d653b63f43cb41","tid":2109380,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:33:39.000Z